<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy and Policy</title>
    <style>
      /* CSS styling here */
      body {
        font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        color: #333;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        color: #333;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        color: #555;
      }

      .policy-section {
        background-color: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0px 0px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 30px;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease;
      }

      .policy-section:hover {
        transform: translateY(-5px);
      }

      .policy-text {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #555;
        text-align: left;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h1>Privacy and Policy</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to our privacy and policy page. At [Glow Melbourne Events], we
          are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring the security of
          your personal information.
        </p>

        <div class="policy-text">
          <p>
            We collect and use your personal information only for providing and
            improving our services. By using our website, you agree to the
            collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>

          <p>
            Your data is safe with us. We do not share your personal information
            with third parties without your explicit consent.
          </p>

          <p>
            Our website may contain links to external sites. We are not
            responsible for the content and privacy practices of these sites, so
            please be aware when you leave our site and read the privacy
            statements of each website that collects personal information.
          </p>

          <p>
            If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy,
            please contact us at [glowmelbourneevents@gmail.com].
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
